snippet.title: Active Soccer 2 DX - Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
The Active Soccer series is back and is now available on PS4 and PS Vita!

www.thefoxsoftware.com

Active Soccer 2 DX is an exciting top-down arcade football game providing a fast-paced arcade experience, implementing amazing playability and simple controls.

http://www.thefoxsoftware.com
